snippet.title: [Solo Leveling:ARISE] Character Teaser #4: Lee Joohee
snippet.description:
A hunter with an angelic heart!

She never turns a blind eye to other hunters in need.
Check out the teaser of B-rank healer 'Lee Joo-hee'!
